21#include "mpc-impl.h"
22
23void
24mpc_set_prec (mpc_t x, mpfr_prec_t prec)
25{
26 mpfr_set_prec (mpc_realref(x), prec);
27 mpfr_set_prec (mpc_imagref(x), prec);
28}
